  "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Processor:</strong>2.4 GHz Quad Core<br>\t</li><li><strong>Memory:</strong>4 GB RAM<br>\t</li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong>1024MB OpenGL 2.1 Compartible</li></ul>"
