  "reviews": "&quot;It’s about momentum, speed, grace under pressure. When I play it, I don’t blink. When I die, I’m never frustrated. In moments when it has me in rapt attention on its dancefloor, it’s the greatest game in the world.&quot;<br>90%, Editor's Choice - <a href=\"http://www.pcgamer.com/review/super-hexagon-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >PC Gamer</a><br>&quot;A masterpiece of design purity.&quot;<br>9/10 - <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.edge-online.com/review/super-hexagon-review-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >EDGE</a><br>&quot;This is the kind of game you’re going to pass off to your friends and say, 'You’ve gotta check this out.' It’s dangerously addictive.&quot;<br>9/10 - <a href=\"http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/09/20/super-hexagon-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >IGN</a>",
