  "supported_languages": "English, Spanish - Spain, French, German, Portuguese - Brazil",
  "reviews": "“Gods Will Be Watching takes adventure games to new, dark, and strategic places.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/07/25/gods-will-be-watching-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >IGN</a><br><br>“...a very clever, very different kind of adventure that will make you feel and make you feel bad...”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"http://www.pcgamer.com/review/gods-will-be-watching-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >PC Gamer</a><br><br>“God Will Be Watching is a fantasy that captures a very real, disturbing hint of apocalyptic reality.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.avclub.com/article/gods-will-be-watching-lays-bare-brutal-reality-apo-207255\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >The AV Club</a><br>",
