  "reviews": "“This levity, this world, and these people are going to be with me forever. If you've ever complained about there being too much violence in gaming, or that games are all the same, and you don't play this... I hope somebody hugs you.”<br>9.5/10 – <a href=\"http://www.destructoid.com/review-dropsy-310645.phtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Destructoid</a><br><br>“...a beautiful, bewildering, unforgettable game of hugs, love, and hollowing sadness.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.thejimquisition.com/2015/09/dropsy-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >The Jimquisition</a><br><br>“Dropsy is a game that warmed my hardened, cynical heart.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://venturebeat.com/2015/09/09/dropsy-is-lovable-despite-some-ugliness/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GamesBeat</a><br>",
