  "detailed_description": "<h1>Digital Deluxe Edition</h1><p>Game + Soundtrack.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Painters Guild is a management sim where you control an art academy in the Italian Renaissance.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Paint artwork as beautiful as the Mona Lisa.<br></li><li>Hire painters like Leonardo da Vinci, Michelangelo and millions of randomly generated artists.<br></li><li>Expand your guild and customize it with furniture and other options.<br></li><li>Play in 3 different cities: Florence, Venice and Rome.</li></ul>",
