  "detailed_description": "<h1>NONGÜNZ IS OUT! THANK YOU!</h1><p><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/633130/extras/actualizaciónpostrelease.JPG?t=1496087100\" ><br><br>Nongünz finally arrives at Steam!! It has been an intense way with a lot of people backing the game, giving Nongünz a lot of love, now we are very happy with the reception of the game, we love there are so much people discovering Nongünz secrets... Now it´s time to play it!!<br><br>The game has all the personality and crazy way of their devs @verz_edu (Producer, Game designer, Main Pixel Artist, and Creative Director) and @ezrubiera (Main Programmer), the music has all the charm and style of @beibeicoli.<br>We also want to thank all those people behind of the development:<br>Marcos a.k.a Muffin de Sepia (an insane level designer) Charly Santafé and Guille Laorga (lovely guys with magic on their hands) &quot;our&quot; Rafer Labarta (keep an eye on this promising guy!) Bakir Khawam a.k.a. Moha (the finnest pixel artist of Persia) <br>For all of you guys, our infinite LOVE &lt;3<br><br>If you want to keep up to date, just follow us:<br><br><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/SindiecateArts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >http://www.twitter.com/SindiecateArts</a><br><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/Brainwash_Gang\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >http://www.twitter.com/Brainwash_Gang</a><br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.facebook.com/Sindiecate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >http://www.facebook.com/Sindiecate</a><br><br>We will be updating and very aware of every comment you made :)<br><br>Now is time to Nongünz!</p><br><h1>Join our DISCORD!</h1><p><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/633130/extras/actualizacion.JPG?t=1496087100\" ><br><br>Chat with Nongünz developers at the DISCORD group we´ve created.<br>You can discover the latest and exclusive info about Nongünz in our channel:<br><br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discord.gg/AUJPTV\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >https://discord.gg/AUJPTV</a><br><br>NONGÜNZ is closer than ever...</p><br><h1>This Friday...We NONGÜNZ!</h1><p><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/633130/extras/ezgif.com-optimize.JPG?t=1496087100\" ><br><br>The release date for Nongünz is really really near and the most early twitchers and youtubers have started to streaming our game.<br><br>You can see NONGÜNZ in action if you follow us or follow Brainwash Gang on Twitter and Facebook.<br><br>Also you can add this game to your wishlist NOW!!<br><br>SAVE THE DATE. MAY 19!!<br><br><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/SindiecateArts\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >http://www.twitter.com/SindiecateArts</a><br><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/Brainwash_Gang\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >http://www.twitter.com/Brainwash_Gang</a><br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.facebook.com/sindiecate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >http://www.facebook.com/sindiecate</a></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Nongünz</strong> is a nihilistic action platformer which combines hectic shootouts with the management of a <strong>mysterious idle game</strong>.<br><br>Each run will have you parting from a black and white graveyard into an ever-changing gothic dungeon full of nightmares fleshed out of human viscera. Surviving this distraught roguelike will not only require skill but style, since Nongünz rewards you for long-lasting combos and challenges... moreover, score will play a key role in the progress of the idle game: the formation of your very own band of lost souls and death cultists.<br><br>As the world of <strong>Nongünz</strong> evolves, you will meet special characters that will inhabit your graveyard: praying cultists, self-scourging martyrs, somber gravediggers... which will either help you widen your killing skills or improve the performance of the insidious idle game built around the graveyard.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unforgiving gameplay that will challenge both your skill and your wits.<br></li><li>The whole game is a riddle. Unveil the mystery behind the nihilistic universe of Nongünz.<br></li><li>Beautifully crafted black and white pixel environments and characters.<br></li><li>Hundreds of levels plagued with dozens of differents enemies.<br></li><li>Many weapons, items and equipment to unlock and master.<br></li><li>The potential to change your perception about existence, violence and mankind.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Nongünz</strong> is a nihilistic action platformer which combines hectic shootouts with the management of a <strong>mysterious idle game</strong>.<br><br>Each run will have you parting from a black and white graveyard into an ever-changing gothic dungeon full of nightmares fleshed out of human viscera. Surviving this distraught roguelike will not only require skill but style, since Nongünz rewards you for long-lasting combos and challenges... moreover, score will play a key role in the progress of the idle game: the formation of your very own band of lost souls and death cultists.<br><br>As the world of <strong>Nongünz</strong> evolves, you will meet special characters that will inhabit your graveyard: praying cultists, self-scourging martyrs, somber gravediggers... which will either help you widen your killing skills or improve the performance of the insidious idle game built around the graveyard.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unforgiving gameplay that will challenge both your skill and your wits.<br></li><li>The whole game is a riddle. Unveil the mystery behind the nihilistic universe of Nongünz.<br></li><li>Beautifully crafted black and white pixel environments and characters.<br></li><li>Hundreds of levels plagued with dozens of differents enemies.<br></li><li>Many weapons, items and equipment to unlock and master.<br></li><li>The potential to change your perception about existence, violence and mankind.</li></ul>",
  "short_description": "Nongünz is a nihilistic action platformer roguelike. Nongünz is obscure in both gameplay and theme. Nongünz is a riddle that demands sacrifice.",
  "supported_languages": "English, French, Italian, German, Spanish - Spain, Simplified Chinese, Korean, Dutch, Japanese, Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese, Portuguese - Brazil, Russian, Swedish, Bulgarian, Czech, Traditional Chinese, Danish, Finnish, Greek, Hungarian, Romanian, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Arabic",
  "reviews": "“This game is wonderfully stylistic and showed a lot of promise”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/tech/nongnz-preview-binding-isaac-meets-10150365\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Daily Mirror</a><br><br>“Nongünz is a hyper-stylized action platformer with some awesome art direction. It's also apparently tough as nails, drawing more than one comparison to Enter the Gungeon.”<br><a href=\"http://www.pcgamer.com/new-steam-games/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >PCGamer</a><br><br>“And it’s hard not to like a game where you’re building an undead band while also clearing out dungeons full of skeletal creatures.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.dualshockers.com/nongunz-nongunz-steam-pc-mac-linux-release/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >DualShockers</a><br>",
